Clean Architecture Layer: Use Cases (Application Business Rules)

Class Name: DogManager

Responsibilities:
- Associates a sprite with a given dog
- Instantiates a DogeCoinCalculator, DogExperienceCalculator, and DogMover for the dog
- Runs the DogMover thread that moves the dog
- Has a pet dog method that calls DogeCoinCalculator and DogExperienceCalculator methods
- Has a method that determines if a mouse click is on the sprite


Collaborators:
- Dog
- Sprite
- DogeCoinCalculator
- DogExperienceCalculator
- DogMover
